reviewText: I like to do my abs daily, this is a very short dvd but level 3 is effective.
The DVD was very inexpensive.  The workout is very short.  Perfect if you want to combine it with another workout or do not have a lot of time, but want to get abs in.  Highly recommend

This is a great workout for the beginner or someone who is coming off of a convelescent period in their life. It wakes up the body parts and gets them ready for more. It combines resistence and stetching.
I use this dvd every once in a while. I haven't seen results but thats because I hardly work out using this. I recommend it if you're going to stick with it.
